The Fleet's Naval Aviation currently consists of:10
689th Independent Fighter Aviation Regiment -
Kaliningrad Chkalovsk - operating Su-27;
4th Independent Naval Assault Aviation Regiment -
Chernyakhovsk Air Base - operating Su-24M/MR;
125th Independent Helicopter Squadron - HQ at Chkalovsk - operating Mi-8, Mi-24 (this was the former 288th Independent Helicopter Regt of the 11th Guards Army and used to be at
Nivenskoye );
396th Independent Shipborne Anti-Submarine Helicopter Squadron -
Donskoye Air Base - Ka-27/PS, Ka-29;
398th Independent Air Transport Squadron - HQ at Khrabrovo - An-2, An-12, An-24, An-26, Be-12, Mi-8.
